bad tupping weather
Homonym Number:
Word Class: phrase
Sense Number:  1
Definition:extreme weather during tupping that causes rams to lose interest in their task.


Origin: [none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain: Rural
Region: [none]
See:
Pronunciation:
